```plantuml
@startuml victorshinya_serverless-chatbot
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor User

rectangle "IBM Cloud" as Cloud {
  rectangle "IBM Cloud Functions" as Functions {
    rectangle "assistant.js" as Assistant #lightblue
    rectangle "mongodb.js" as MongoDB #lightgreen
  }

  rectangle "Watson Assistant" as Watson #lightpink
  database "MongoDB" as DB #lightyellow
}

User -> Functions : Send message
Functions -> Assistant : Trigger assistant.js
Assistant -> Watson : Process input
Watson -> Assistant : Return response
Assistant -> MongoDB : Store conversation data
MongoDB -> DB : Save data
Assistant -> Functions : Return user response
Functions -> User : Send response
@enduml
```